Scripts for testing cross-language interfacing (primarily to R) as part
of a new 2018 edition of 'Evolutionary Genomics':

Genetical Genomics for Evolutionary Studies by Pjotr Prins Geert Smant
and Ritsert C. Jansen, chapter 19 in Evolutionary Genomics:
statistical and computational methods, ed. Anisimova M. within
Meth. Mol. Biol. Series of Humana-Springer 2012

Sharing programming resources between Bio* projects through remote
procedure call and native call stack strategies, by Pjotr Prins,
Naohisa Goto, Andrew Yates, Laurent Gautier, Scooter Willis,
Christopher Fields and Toshiaki Katayama, chapter 21 in Evolutionary
Genomics: statistical and computational methods, ed. Anisimova
M. within Meth. Mol. Biol. Series of Humana-Springer 2012

Scalable Computing for Evolutionary Genomics by Pjotr Prins, Dominique
Belhachemi, Steffen MÃ¶ller and Geert Smant, chapter 22 in
Evolutionary Genomics: statistical and computational methods,
ed. Anisimova M. within Meth. Mol. Biol. Series of Humana-Springer
2012

See the document in ./doc for more information on running these
scripts.

